if this is a negotiation or a threat.

154
00:13:45,824 --> 00:13:48,034
Does your dear friend know

155
00:13:48,618 --> 00:13:49,869
that his death

156
00:13:51,746 --> 00:13:53,373
is being used like this?

157
00:13:53,456 --> 00:13:55,708
He'd be proud

158
00:13:57,293 --> 00:13:58,837
