159
00:14:01,548 --> 00:14:03,091
It wasn't exploitation.

160
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:05,635
He let himself be used.

161
00:14:08,763 --> 00:14:11,850
Just so I could have something
to shake you with

162
00:14:12,392 --> 00:14:13,560
