you to understand.

165
00:14:57,645 --> 00:14:59,397
What the heck did you do?

166
00:15:01,691 --> 00:15:03,693
Say something.

167
00:15:04,444 --> 00:15:05,528
If I tell you

168
00:15:06,446 --> 00:15:08,364
can you handle it?

169
00:15:09,324 --> 00:15:10,325
Tell me.

170
00:15:11,242 --> 00:15:13,786
