- What should I have done, then?

179
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:37,936
How long are you
going to live like that?

180
00:15:38,019 --> 00:15:39,771
I'm sick of it, too.

181
00:15:39,854 --> 00:15:40,855
Jun-seo.

182
00:15:41,439 --> 00:15:43,358
Now that Jae-oh ended up like that

183
00:15:44,192 --> 00:15:45,777
I can't stop anymore.

184
00:15:46,694 --> 00:15:48,488
Is this all my fault?

185
00:15:50,281 --> 00:15:52,367
Who has the right to condemn me?

186
00:15:53,451 --> 00:15:55,244
Who can understand

187
00:15:55,620 --> 00:15:58,456
my situation and my position
right now?

188
00:15:59,123 --> 00:16:00,792
Then, answer me this one thing.

189
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:04,087
You can stop now.

190
00:16:06,673 --> 00:16:09,175
This is the end, right?

191
00:16:15,473 --> 00:16:16,474
Right?

192
00:16:17,183 --> 00:16:18,726
Please say something.

193
00:16:19,769 --> 00:16:22,480
Please tell me that this is the end!

194
00:16:24,232 --> 00:16:25,650
I can't stop.

195
00:16:27,068 --> 00:16:28,319
I won't stop.

196
00:16:30,238 --> 00:16:33,449
