where my name is barely mentioned

216
00:18:08,044 --> 00:18:09,087
won't...

217
00:18:09,170 --> 00:18:10,588
- Do we get rid of this, too?
- What's this?

218
00:18:10,671 --> 00:18:11,672
It's his phone.

219
00:18:11,756 --> 00:18:12,882
You can give it to me.

220
