241
00:19:17,947 --> 00:19:19,198
Leave Ah-jin alone.

242
00:19:21,576 --> 00:19:23,661
I'll be the one to stop her.

243
00:19:24,662 --> 00:19:27,832
You just take a step back
and watch from afar.

244
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:30,585
Just like you always have.

245
00:19:49,854 --> 00:19:51,397
I've come to make a confession.

246
00:19:55,276 --> 00:19:57,361
